{"tid":1487784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手推畀外國We Are Hong Konger","createTime":"2019-08-19T11:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T14:07:35.000Z","uid":44277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d43eacc3ec6501557af7e0974de6fcf08178b049","tid":1487784,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"Please forward:<br />\n<br />\nHong Kongers have demonstrated utmost perseverance and determination to bravely pursue freedom under authoritarianism.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Hong Konger&quot; is no longer defined by where one is located. &quot;Hong Konger&quot; represents people who value 'courage' and 'freedom'. We sincerely hope every one who upholds this exact same belief can show your support to all Hong Kongers by sharing the tag #WeAreHongKonger on social media. <br />\n<br />\nFrom now on, people who    love freedom and courage are all &quot;Hong Konger&quot;, no matter who you are, where you are from.<br />\n<br />\n#WeAreHongKonger<br />\n<br />\n請轉發：<br />\n香港人已經展示出無比的堅毅和決心，在強權之下，仍勇敢地追求自由。<br />\n<br />\n香港人不再是地域上的觀念，而是代表「勇氣」和「自由」，希望世界每一位堅持同一信念的人，用你任何的方法表達對香港人的支持，放上你的社交媒體，並 #WeAreHongKonger。<br />\n<br />\n從今以後，再沒有人種界限，也沒有國界，只有熱愛自由和勇敢的Hong Konger。<br />\n<br />\n#WeAreHongKonger"},{"pid":"bd3fd6ad531b2bcd214a9b4fcd7e9a32ffa4c491","tid":1487784,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<strong>解放軍係10分鐘之內就可以落黎軍管香港<br />\n美國可以一夜之間取消香港關係法<br />\n隨便一樣野都足以致命<br />\n令所有外資撤退，港元急速貶值</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"8241e73fdc487a2578712db2fce835459063b83b","tid":1487784,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"